        "message": "LU-11394 osd-zfs: rename ZFS_MAJOR et al\n\nZFS_MINOR, used for the ZFS minor version, conflicts with a macro\ndefined within zfs.\n\nZFS_MINOR was added to zfsonlinux by commit a6cc9756, and is used\nthere for the device minor number.  Rename the Lustre macro\nZFS_VER_MAJOR, and make the similar change to ZFS_MAJOR, ZFS_PATCH,\nand ZFS_FIX for naming consistency.\n\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Faaland <faaland1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Ie6f7445042ef5be5377be04871724b36452e94b9\n"
